"宋体\">～</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">0.15mg</font><font face=\"宋体\">。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \">\r\n		<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">儿童每日需用量<font face=\"Times New Roman\">0.03</font><font face=\"宋体\">～</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">0.1mg</font><font face=\"宋体\">。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \">\r\n		<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">【副作用】</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \">\r\n		<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">过量的钼可引起不良反应。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \">\r\n		<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">【注意事项】</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \">\r\n		<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">每日摄取量超过<font face=\"Times New Roman\">0.54mg</font><font face=\"宋体\">，钼可增加铜从尿中排出。超过</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">10</font><font face=\"宋体\">～</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">15mg</font><font face=\"宋体\">时，则可出现痛风综合症。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n	<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \">\r\n		<span style=\"mso-spac